I".<p>Let’s declutter the closet while the weather is nice!</p>

<p>You may ask, where do the clothes go after the decluttering❓ What do I do with the clothes?</p>

<p>You can choose to either sell or donate❗️</p>

<p>👉🏻Options if you would like to sell:</p>

<p>1️⃣Home garage sale (Garage Sale)</p>

<p>2️⃣ online platform sale (Kjiji/ Marketplace/ EBay)</p>

<p>3️⃣ Affordable thrift store sales (Common Sort/ Stile Encore/ Plato’s Closet, etc.)</p>

<p>4️⃣ high-end thrift store consignment sales (Consignment Store, etc.)</p>

<p>👉🏻If you would like to ♻️Recycle Through Donations:</p>

<p>1️⃣H&amp;M (get up to 15% off coupon for one item)</p>

<p>2️⃣Uniqlo Uniqlo</p>

<p>3️⃣Major supermarkets/Plaza/Mall donation boxes</p>

<p>4️⃣Special donation object organizations (such as Dress for woman/ Covenant House/ Jessie’s Centre/ Horizons For Young etc.)</p>

<p>🌟Whichever way you choose, Teal Decluttering can assistant and guide you along the process. Please get in touch with us if you would like to know more 😊</p>

<p>👍🏻Here’s a shout out to our customer from Oshawa, who did a great job of donating 4 large bags of clothes to Diabetes Canada.</p>

